name: Open Gag Mouth
description:
This is my first LoRa-model.
v1.0
I think that it is kinda overtrained and not perfect, but still allows you to perform a sufficient number of manipulations.

Tips: 0.6 - 0.8 scale will be good
training model (also used to generation): abyssorangemix2_Hard
Keywords: open gag mouth

v2.0
Complete model overhaul, from learning model to learning level. Gronon helped me with changing numbers and stuff for this version of the model.

Tips: 1 scale must be good, for better results u can use 768x768 resolution
Training model: NAI
Images generated on model: abyssorangemix2_Hard
Keywords: circle gag mouth

If you want to help me with learning how to create LoRA models, or learn to create models with me - please join my server in discord, my goal is to create a friendly community that will help each other to achieve high quality training for LoRA models.
discord.gg/vmVzJQEhqy


If u know how to improve model, let me know
